[
  {
    "startTime": 0.11,
    "endTime": 1.24,
    "text": "Who was it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.24,
    "endTime": 2.12,
    "text": "Who was what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.12,
    "endTime": 3.3600000000000003,
    "text": "Who was that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.36,
    "endTime": 4.9399999999999995,
    "text": "Oh, my grandmother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.94,
    "endTime": 8.56,
    "text": "Oh, okay. Well, I'll...."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.56,
    "endTime": 9.850000000000001,
    "text": "Good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.85,
    "endTime": 14.309999999999999,
    "text": "And you know... I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.31,
    "endTime": 15.100000000000001,
    "text": "What for?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.64,
    "endTime": 18.59,
    "text": "For your loss."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.59,
    "endTime": 21.04,
    "text": "Why are you sorry? Did you kill her?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.04,
    "endTime": 22.93,
    "text": "I'm just being polite, mate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.93,
    "endTime": 24.96,
    "text": "It's another worn out cliche."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.96,
    "endTime": 27.12,
    "text": "You're not sorry — you didn't know my grandmother!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.12,
    "endTime": 29.12,
    "text": "Why would you be sorry that she is dead?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.12,
    "endTime": 32.38,
    "text": "It's a bastardization of the language."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.38,
    "endTime": 34.86,
    "text": "You're right. I couldn't care less she's dead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.86,
    "endTime": 38.93,
    "text": "There. Now that doesn't have feel fresher? The clean air of honesty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.93,
    "endTime": 40.17,
    "text": "I'm glad she's dead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.17,
    "endTime": 42.27,
    "text": "- Why would you be glad? - I, I got carried away, it's..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.27,
    "endTime": 43.49,
    "text": "You are indifferent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.49,
    "endTime": 45.24,
    "text": "You didn't know my grandmother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.24,
    "endTime": 48.36,
    "text": "You are indifferent to her life and death."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.36,
    "endTime": 49.87,
    "text": "That is proper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.8,
    "endTime": 56.44,
    "text": "Sorry about saying I'm glad, not about her death."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.44,
    "endTime": 59.559999999999995,
    "text": "About which you are...?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.56,
    "endTime": 60.7,
    "text": "Indifferent?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.65,
    "endTime": 68.56,
    "text": "Dick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.56,
    "endTime": 69.51,
    "text": "I can hear you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.51,
    "endTime": 72.80000000000001,
    "text": "Sorry, but not about your dead nan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.92,
    "endTime": 82.87,
    "text": "Look, can I ask you something? A serious question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.87,
    "endTime": 84.64,
    "text": "Quickly, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.64,
    "endTime": 86.78,
    "text": "Why aren't you upset about your gran?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.78,
    "endTime": 88.87,
    "text": "What makes you think I'm not upset?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.87,
    "endTime": 91.62,
    "text": "Well, normally people are affected by a loss."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.62,
    "endTime": 93.35000000000001,
    "text": "They show it in some way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.35,
    "endTime": 94.55,
    "text": "What about your nan?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.55,
    "endTime": 97.67,
    "text": "She was an extraordinary woman, and her loss afire in my soul."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.67,
    "endTime": 98.52,
    "text": "Tell your face."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.52,
    "endTime": 99.58999999999999,
    "text": "Tell my face what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.59,
    "endTime": 102.51,
    "text": "Normally people... cry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.51,
    "endTime": 104.67,
    "text": "I can't afford to cry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.67,
    "endTime": 110.78,
    "text": "Look, I could break down now in front of you, rivers of tears, and fall into your arms, and then what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.78,
    "endTime": 112.15,
    "text": "Well, then you'd feel better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.15,
    "endTime": 113.26,
    "text": "I'm a great cuddle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.26,
    "endTime": 115.52000000000001,
    "text": "Look, I've got lovely big mom tits. Come on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.52,
    "endTime": 117.35,
    "text": "- Oh, God.  - Come on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.35,
    "endTime": 121.33,
    "text": "But then all the emotion will be used up, wasted!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.33,
    "endTime": 127.72,
    "text": "My grandmother would be buried, and I'd sit down to try and describe the pain, and there'd be nothing left!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.72,
    "endTime": 132.18,
    "text": "You can't use everything that you go through in life for a... book!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.18,
    "endTime": 134.56,
    "text": "Sometimes you've just got to... be!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.56,
    "endTime": 138.93,
    "text": "I think my grandmother deserves more than a spontaneous howl of anguish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.93,
    "endTime": 141.66,
    "text": "She deserves a novella at least."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.66,
    "endTime": 146.64,
    "text": "So, I shall push it down. I either cry, or I write."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.64,
    "endTime": 150.54,
    "text": "Hmph. Well, doesn't sound very healthy to me."
  }
]